@startuml
object Student
object AuthController
object LinkStudentDiscordUseCase
object CredentialStore
object StudentDiscordIdentityStore
object DiscordOAuth
Student --> AuthController : 1: callback code/state
AuthController --> LinkStudentDiscordUseCase : 2: handleCallback
LinkStudentDiscordUseCase --> CredentialStore : 3: load OAuth credential
LinkStudentDiscordUseCase --> LinkStudentDiscordUseCase : 4: verify signed state
LinkStudentDiscordUseCase --> DiscordOAuth : 5: exchange code
LinkStudentDiscordUseCase --> DiscordOAuth : 6: fetch current user
LinkStudentDiscordUseCase --> StudentDiscordIdentityStore : 7: upsert identity and token
LinkStudentDiscordUseCase --> AuthController : 8: success/cancelled
AuthController --> Student : 9: HTML postMessage + close
@enduml
